***** When the terminal freezes by pressing “ctrl + s”
	Then I can unfreezes it by pressing “ctrl + q”


A) install linux like terminal emulator ‘CMDER-full’
	* link : http://cmder.net/ 


B) construct linux-like environments in windows ‘Cygwin’ or ‘MinGW’
	1) Cygwin	
	* link : https://cygwin.com/install.html

	2) MinGW
	* link : https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw/files/latest/download?source=files 


C) install ‘Apache + MySQL + PHP’ 



D) install ‘JAVA 9’ - jdk, jre
	* link : http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk9-downloads-3848520.html 

	*** Add jre location to the PATH(=SYSTEM VARIABLES) ***
	


E) install ‘Eclipse IDE’
	* link : http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/eclipse-packages/ 


F) install ‘Python 3’ 
	* link : https://www.python.org/downloads/ 


G) install ‘Visual Studio Code’ 
	* link : https://code.visualstudio.com/download 


H) install mouse hovering manager 'WizMouse' 
	* link : http://antibody-software.com/web/software/software/wizmouse-makes-your-mouse-wheel-work-on-the-window-under-the-mouse/ 


I) install Clipboard Manager 'ShapeShifter'
	* link : https://github.com/ffMathy/Shapeshifter 


J) install search tool ‘Everything’ 
	* link : https://www.voidtools.com/














